    "MeasurePrefix": "SB",
    "MeasureNumber": 342,
    "CatchLine": "Requires agency, board, commission or other instrumentality of state that lawfully seizes firearm to transfer firearm to Department of State Lands for disposition as unclaimed property.",
    "MinorityCatchLine": null,
    "MeasureSummary": "\tRequires agency, board, commission or other instrumentality of state that lawfully seizes firearm to transfer firearm to Department of State Lands for disposition as unclaimed property. Requires department to deposit proceeds of sale of firearm into Emergency Housing Account and directs Housing and Community Services Department to disburse moneys deposited for purposes of assisting persons who are homeless or at risk of becoming homeless.",
    "CurrentVersion": null,
    "RelatingToFull": "Relating to the disposition of firearms lawfully seized by the state; creating new provisions; and amending ORS 131.597, 131A.350 and 166.279.",
